<i>noun</i>: 노출증 [노출쯩] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>노출증 [노출쯩]</dt><br>
<dd>exhibitionism</dd><br>
<dd>자기의 육체, 특히 성기를 남에게 보임으로써 쾌감을 얻으려는 정신 이상.</dd><br>
<dd>A mental disorder in which a person feels good when showing others his/her body, especially the genitals.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>